modName: RaceMenu preset of my Breton character Hannah
summary: RaceMenu preset of my Breton character Hannah
descriptionHtml:
RaceMenupreset of my Breton character Hannah.

So I returned to Skyrim after some time, and made a new char. Being quite happy with
the looks, I decided to share the preset.

Requiredmods:
SKSE:  [url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]http://skse.silverlock.org/[/url]
RaceMenu:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/[/url]?

Install: 
simplymerge the contents of the zip with your data folder.

Use:
Open theconsole (~)
Type showracemenu
Close console (~)
Goto tab “Presets"
Click “Load preset” (F9)
Select Hannah preset, which should load my preset
Go back to “Sliders” tab
Make adjustments if you want (…nah..)
Click “Done”
Name your char

The additional mods that I used to get the looks as in the image are (installed in that order):
Coverwomen(look 4):  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3563/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3563/[/url]?
The Eyes of Beauty:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/[/url]?
SG Fem Eyebrows:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/[/url]?
Pretty Lips:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1167/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1167/[/url]?
LiFEv1 UNP-UNPB:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26354/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26354/[/url]?
